  "original_title": "\u0b89\u0bb2\u0b95 \u0b89\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Head of the World Food Program is coming to Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The World Food Program and the World Food and Agriculture Organization are jointly investigating the food crisis situation in Sri Lanka. Similarly, Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe told the meeting that the head of the World Food Program will visit Sri Lanka next week on my invitation.",
        "We have launched a program to increase food availability in collaboration with the World Food Program and the Food and Agriculture Organization. Currently, their delegation is studying Sri Lanka's food crisis, he said.",
        "And we have to think afresh about such companies which have become a burden to the country and people. Is it fair to burden people like this for thirty or forty years? Should we continue to burden the people and run these institutions? Why can't the services offered by these companies be made available to people without burden? Aren't there other ways to provide these services? Considering all these facts, we are taking immediate steps to restructure these companies.",
        "It will be ensured that they are maintained so as not to burden the country. He said many more issues need to be addressed in our journey forward to overcome the current challenges."
      ],
